    {"type":"text","id":"before_c","x":18,"y":66,"width":399,"height":192,"text":"statement = assignment | increment | decrement\n\nassignment = identifier \"=\" expr \";\"\nincrement  = identifier \"++\" \";\"\ndecrement  = identifier \"--\" \";\"\n\nProblema al parsear  x += 1:\n  Veo \"x\" (identifier)\n  ¿Es assignment, increment o decrement?\n  NO SÉ — todos empiezan con identifier\n\n  Parser intenta assignment → lee = → OK, continúa\n  Parser intenta increment → lee = → FALLA → backtrack\n  Parser intenta decrement → lee = → FALLA → backtrack\n\nResultado: backtracking O(n) por alternativa — COSTOSO\n❌ No es LL(1) — requiere lookahead indefinido","originalText":"statement = assignment | increment | decrement\n\nassignment = identifier \"=\" expr \";\"\nincrement  = identifier \"++\" \";\"\ndecrement  = identifier \"--\" \";\"\n\nProblema al parsear  x += 1:\n  Veo \"x\" (identifier)\n  ¿Es assignment, increment o decrement?\n  NO SÉ — todos empiezan con identifier\n\n  Parser intenta assignment → lee = → OK, continúa\n  Parser intenta increment → lee = → FALLA → backtrack\n  Parser intenta decrement → lee = → FALLA → backtrack\n\nResultado: backtracking O(n) por alternativa — COSTOSO\n❌ No es LL(1) — requiere lookahead indefinido","fontSize":11,"fontFamily":3,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","strokeColor":"#991b1b","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"seed":15,"version":1,"versionNonce":16,"isDeleted":false,"groupIds":[],"boundElements":null,"link":null,"locked":false,"containerId":null,"lineHeight":1.4},

