    {"type":"text","id":"after_c","x":473,"y":66,"width":399,"height":192,"text":"statement = identifier statement_rest\n\nstatement_rest = \"=\" expr \";\"    ← assignment\n               | \"++\" \";\"         ← increment\n               | \"--\" \";\"         ← decrement\n\nParseo de  x = 1:\n  Veo \"x\" → leer identifier → OK\n  Llegar a statement_rest\n  Veo \"=\" → es assignment → aplicar regla 1\n  No hay ambigüedad, no hay backtrack ✓\n\nParseo de  x++:\n  Veo \"x\" → leer identifier → OK\n  Llegar a statement_rest\n  Veo \"++\" → es increment → aplicar regla 2 ✓\n\n✓ LL(1): una sola decisión por token consumido","originalText":"statement = identifier statement_rest\n\nstatement_rest = \"=\" expr \";\"    ← assignment\n               | \"++\" \";\"         ← increment\n               | \"--\" \";\"         ← decrement\n\nParseo de  x = 1:\n  Veo \"x\" → leer identifier → OK\n  Llegar a statement_rest\n  Veo \"=\" → es assignment → aplicar regla 1\n  No hay ambigüedad, no hay backtrack ✓\n\nParseo de  x++:\n  Veo \"x\" → leer identifier → OK\n  Llegar a statement_rest\n  Veo \"++\" → es increment → aplicar regla 2 ✓\n\n✓ LL(1): una sola decisión por token consumido","fontSize":11,"fontFamily":3,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","strokeColor":"#065f46","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"seed":35,"version":1,"versionNonce":36,"isDeleted":false,"groupIds":[],"boundElements":null,"link":null,"locked":false,"containerId":null,"lineHeight":1.4}
